  "body": "### Description\r\n\r\n*Type*: Bug\r\n*Summary*: \r\nwhen you start a chat with user A and than user A set up or change profile photo - it does not affect to Chats with user A.\r\n\r\n#### Expected behavior\r\nuser avatar is updated in \"Chats\"\r\n\r\n#### Actual behavior\r\nuser avatar leaves the same\r\n![dev_ava](https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/4557972/34101579-ca093a54-e3ee-11e7-801d-e68aa3010192.png)\r\n\r\n\r\n### Reproduction\r\n\r\n- Open Status with user B\r\n- start chat with user A\r\n- change profile photo in user A account\r\n- check  \"Chats\" tab in user B account\r\n- reopen app\r\n- check  \"Chats\" tab in user B account\r\n\r\n### Additional Information\r\n\r\n* Status version: \r\n nightly 18/12 develop build.\r\n0.9.10-458-ga7f8526c+ \r\n\r\n\r\n* Operating System: Android, iOS\r\nreproducible for real GalaxyS7, IPhone 7\r\n\r\n",
